---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Resources | Level Up" description="Resources and media guidelines from Level Up's campaigns on domestic abuse, pregnancy in prison, abortion, and hair relaxers.">

  <!-- Hero Banner -->
  <section id="sub-page-hero-banner" class="hero-banner">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <h2 class="hero-title">Resources</h2>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Resources Grid Section -->
  <section class="resources-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="resources-grid">

        <article class="resource-card">
          <a href="/ddw-resources" class="card-image-link">
            <img
              src="https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/result-1-1.webp"
              alt="Dignity for Dead Women — media guidelines resources"
              width="720"
              height="405"
            />
          </a>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title"><a href="/ddw-resources">DDW Resources</a></h3>
            <p class="card-description">In consultation with domestic violence experts and victims&rsquo; families, Level Up produced the UK&rsquo;s first media guidelines on reporting domestic abuse deaths &mdash; endorsed by IPSO and IMPRESS. Using the AIDA framework, we have trained over 500 journalists.</p>
            <a href="/ddw-resources" class="card-link">View DDW Resources &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="resource-card">
          <a href="/pp-resources" class="card-image-link">
            <img
              src="https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/result.webp"
              alt="End imprisonment of pregnant women — resources"
              width="456"
              height="720"
            />
          </a>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title"><a href="/pp-resources">Pregnancy in Prison Resources</a></h3>
            <p class="card-description">Prison is never a safe place to be pregnant. Following baby deaths in women&rsquo;s prisons, Level Up has produced open letters, sentencing submissions and briefing notes from 2022 to 2025 calling for an end to imprisonment of pregnant women.</p>
            <a href="/pp-resources" class="card-link">View Pregnancy in Prison Resources &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="resource-card">
          <a href="/abortion-is-healthcare-resources" class="card-image-link">
            <img
              src="https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Screenshot-2024-06-04-at-22-1.webp"
              alt="Abortion Is Healthcare — media guidelines resources"
              width="792"
              height="610"
            />
          </a>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title"><a href="/abortion-is-healthcare-resources">Abortion Is Healthcare Resources</a></h3>
            <p class="card-description">With prosecutions for ending a pregnancy rising, media discourse shapes public opinion. Level Up created guidelines for journalists on reporting abortion &mdash; developed with medical experts, abortion providers and journalists.</p>
            <a href="/abortion-is-healthcare-resources" class="card-link">View Abortion Is Healthcare Resources &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="resource-card">
          <a href="/nomorelyes-relaxer-info-kit" class="card-image-link">
            <img
              src="https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Copy-of-NoMoreLyes_FINAL-18-1-scaled-1.webp"
              alt="#NoMoreLyes hair relaxer research kit"
              width="1000"
              height="1500"
            />
          </a>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title"><a href="/nomorelyes-relaxer-info-kit">#NoMoreLyes Relaxer Info Kit</a></h3>
            <p class="card-description">Since Level Up&rsquo;s #NoMoreLyes campaign launched in 2021, a growing body of research from Oxford and Boston universities links hair relaxers to uterine cancer, fibroids and respiratory disease. This kit collects that research.</p>
            <a href="/nomorelyes-relaxer-info-kit" class="card-link">View #NoMoreLyes Resources &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0D0A3E;
    --lime: #CBFF32;
    --cream: #EDEBD2;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .hero-banner {
    min-height: 300px;
    background-color: var(--navy);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.8em 0;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 1130px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px 20px;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'blogh', 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3vw;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream);
    text-align: center;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1130px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .resources-section {
    background-color: var(--cream);
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .resources-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .resource-card {
    background-color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    transition: all 200ms ease-in-out;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .resource-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .card-image-link {
    display: block;
  }

  .card-image-link img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center center;
    display: block;
  }

  .card-body {
    padding: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 22px;
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }

  .card-title a {
    color: var(--navy);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .card-title a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .card-description {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .card-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--lime);
    padding-bottom: 1px;
    width: fit-content;
    margin-top: auto;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .card-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--navy);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .hero-banner {
      padding: 3.5em 0;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.5vw;
    }

    .resources-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 7vw;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .resources-section {
      padding: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    .resources-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
